#

Gala Apple Oatmeal

15 min
$2.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy (if using milk)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastHealthyQuick

Description

A warm, comforting bowl of oatmeal topped with sweet Gala apples and a hint of cinnamon. Perfect for a nutritious breakfast!

Ingredients

  • rolled oats: 1 cup
  • water or milk: 2 cups
  • gala apple: 1, chopped
  • honey or maple syrup: 1 tablespoon
  • cinnamon: 1/2 teaspoon
  • salt: a pinch
